mods.abstract: Invoice for an order placed by Audrey Williams Enterprises for 100 two color window cards (undated) for a performance by Jimmy Martin and the Sunny Mountain Boys. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
